SAN DIEGO GAS & ELECTRIC COMPANY, Petitioner,
v.
CALIFORNIA PUBLIC UTILITIES COMMISSION. No. 18-1368 Supreme Court of the United States. October 7, 2019

Motion of Southern California Edison Company for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Motion of Edison Electric Institute for leave to file a brief as amicus curiae granted. Motion of Shareholders in California Investor-Owned Utilities for leave to file a brief as amici curiae granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the Court of Appeal of California, Fourth Appellate District, Division One denied.
